name: Add-On Popularity
query:
SELECT `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`.item AS "Add-On Item:Link/Airplane Ticket Add-on Item:350", COUNT(`tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`.item) AS "Sold Count:Int:100"
FROM `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`
GROUP BY  `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`.item 
ORDER BY COUNT(`tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`.item) DESC;
